HAN NA-HYUN, HAN SO-HYUN

23
00:02:16,845 --> 00:02:18,972
AUGUST 20, 1997
IT RAINED SO I WORE MY RAINCOAT…

24
00:02:26,521 --> 00:02:27,522
AUGUST 12, 2008

25
00:02:31,985 --> 00:02:33,278
My dear So-hyun

26
00:02:34,404 --> 00:02:35,947
