27
00:02:37,157 --> 00:02:39,868
HIGH SCHOOL GIRL JUMPS IN
AT THE MOMENT OF CRISIS

28
00:02:53,256 --> 00:02:54,257
Wow.

29
00:02:55,258 --> 00:02:56,759
